snippet.title: GWENT: Iron Judgment | Expansion Trailer
snippet.description: Bow before your rightful king! Iron Judgment — Newest GWENT Expansion Arriving on October 2 The North is on the rise and Radovid is back to bring justice to his enemies. Stand by his side or defy royal authority — whichever you choose, get ready for some of the fiercest battles in GWENT’s history.
